---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../../css/services.css";
---

<Layout
  title="Custom Software Development | GeneralSoft UAE"
  description="Expert custom software development services in the UAE. We build scalable, secure, and user-centric web and mobile applications tailored to your business needs."
  path="/services/custom-software/"
  image="/img/og-custom-software.jpg"
>
  <section class="service-content" id="software-services">
    <div class="service-section" style="margin-top: 120px;">
      <h2 class="service-title">Custom Software Development</h2>
      <p>
        In today's fast-paced digital economy, off-the-shelf software rarely meets the unique requirements of a growing business. 
        At GeneralSoft, we design and build custom software solutions that align perfectly with your workflows, data structures, 
        and strategic objectives. Based in Ras Al Khaimah and serving clients across the UAE, our team brings deep technical 
        expertise to every project — from enterprise resource planning systems to customer-facing web applications.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our development process follows industry best practices: requirements gathering, architecture design, iterative 
        development with continuous integration, thorough testing, and seamless deployment. We use modern frameworks and 
        cloud-native architectures to ensure your software is scalable, maintainable, and secure from day one.
      </p>

      <h3>Our Development Approach</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Discovery & Planning</h4>
          <p>We start by understanding your business goals, user needs, and technical requirements to create a comprehensive project roadmap.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Agile Development</h4>
          <p>Our iterative approach delivers working software in regular sprints, allowing for feedback and adjustments throughout the process.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Quality Assurance</h4>
          <p>Automated testing, code reviews, and performance benchmarking ensure your software meets the highest quality standards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Deployment & Support</h4>
          <p>We handle deployment to your infrastructure or cloud platform and provide ongoing maintenance and support.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Technologies We Use</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Frontend: React, Angular, Vue.js, Astro</li>
        <li>Backend: Node.js, Python, .NET Core, Java</li>
        <li>Databases: PostgreSQL, MySQL, MongoDB, SQL Server</li>
        <li>Cloud: AWS, Azure, Google Cloud Platform</li>
        <li>DevOps: Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD pipelines</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Projects Proof Section -->
      <div class="projects-proof">
        <h3>Proven Delivery — Projects Completed</h3>
        <p>
          Our portfolio spans three decades of custom software delivery across
          industries and geographies. Here are representative projects that
          demonstrate our engineering depth.
        </p>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>ERP Solution for Elahi Electronics</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Jun 2009 – Nov 2010</span>
            <span class="role">Architect & Lead Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Designed and implemented a complete Small & Medium Enterprise (SME)
            ERP solution covering authentication, authorization, and
            role-based access in SharePoint using FBA. Built a rich interface
            application in Silverlight with WCF RIA Services as the ERP client.
            Developed business intelligence using SQL Server Analysis Services
            (SSAS) and ETL pipelines using SSIS. Integrated enterprise search
            with FAST Search for SharePoint (FS4SP) with multilingual word
            translation capabilities.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">C#</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">SQL Server 2008 R2</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">SSIS</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">SSAS</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">SharePoint</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">WCF RIA</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">BizTalk 2009</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Loan Workflow Application — Major Bank</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Jan 2006 – Sep 2006</span>
            <span class="role">Architect & Lead Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Developed proof-of-concept loan workflow applications for a large
            bank, integrating Windows Server 2003, WSS, BizTalk 2006, and
            Fuego. Built custom controls for hosting Microsoft Office documents
            inside a browser for seamless integration with BEA's WebLogic
            Portal. The solution automated loan origination, document
            management, and approval workflows.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">BizTalk 2006</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">SharePoint</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">InfoPath</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">WebLogic</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Workflow</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Enterprise Content Management — Hospitality</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Jun 2007 – Aug 2007</span>
            <span class="role">Architect & Lead Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Created a corporate ECM system for 22,000+ employees in the
            hospitality industry. Used extensive BizTalk reflection to reverse
            engineer documentation for the ECM. Authored a 390-page training
            manual for the system. The solution managed enterprise-wide content
            lifecycle, compliance documentation, and knowledge management.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">SharePoint 2007 ECM</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">C#</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">.NET 3.5</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">BizTalk</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>App For Hygiene Service Providers</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Sep 2021 – Dec 2022</span>
            <span class="role">Media Consultant & Trainer. Web & App Developer.</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Developed a cross-platform mobile application for hygiene service
            providers in Abu Dhabi. Built with Flutter and a microservices
            backend architecture. The app manages service scheduling, customer
            management, and real-time service tracking.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">Flutter</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Microservices</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Mobile</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Firebase</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faq-section">

    <div class="container">
      <div class="faq-container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Common questions about our custom software development process in the UAE.</p>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <details>
            <summary>How long does it take to build custom software?</summary>
            <p>Timelines vary based on complexity. A typical web application takes 8–16 weeks, while larger enterprise systems may take 4–8 months. We provide a detailed timeline after the discovery phase.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary>Do you provide ongoing maintenance after launch?</summary>
            <p>Yes. We offer flexible maintenance and support packages to keep your software running smoothly, including bug fixes, security updates, and feature enhancements.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary>Can you integrate with our existing systems?</summary>
            <p>Absolutely. We have extensive experience integrating with third-party APIs, legacy systems, ERPs, and CRMs to ensure seamless data flow across your technology stack.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-content">
        <h2>Let's Build Something Great Together</h2>
        <p>Ready to transform your business with custom software? Get in touch with our team today.</p>
        <div class="contact-info">
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="contact-item-icon">🌐</div><strong>Website</strong><a href="https://generalsoft.ae">generalsoft.ae</a>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <a href="/contact/"><div class="contact-item-icon">📧</div><strong>Contact Us</strong><br />Get in touch</a>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="contact-item-icon">📍</div><strong>Location</strong><span>Ras Al Khaimah</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
